530
00:31:56,900 --> 00:31:58,910
Mr Monkford hired the car from you yesterday.

531
00:31:58,910 --> 00:31:59,860
Yeah, lovely motor.

532
00:31:59,860 --> 00:32:02,860
Mazda RX8. Wouldn't mind one of them myself.

