544
00:32:23,900 --> 00:32:26,100
I've no idea what happened to him. Poor sod!

545
00:32:26,100 --> 00:32:27,930
- Nice holiday, Mr. Ewart?  - Eh?

546
00:32:27,930 --> 00:32:29,220
You've been away, haven't you?

547
00:32:29,220 --> 00:32:32,540
Oh, the... no, it's sun beds, I'm afraid.

548
00:32:32,540 --> 00:32:33,780
Too busy to get away.

549
00:32:33,780 --> 00:32:36,540
My wife would love it, though - bit of sun.

550
00:32:36,540 --> 00:32:38,730
