00:32:38,730 --> 00:32:41,580
I noticed one on the way and I haven't got any change and I'm gasping.

552
00:32:46,700 --> 00:32:48,420
No, sorry.

553
00:32:48,420 --> 00:32:52,540
Oh, well! Thank you very much for your time, Mr. Ewart.

554
00:32:52,540 --> 00:32:55,020
You've been very helpful. Come on, John!

555
00:32:56,620 --> 00:32:58,920
I've got change, if you still want to...

