559
00:33:41,140 --> 00:33:42,140
Hello.

560
00:33:43,100 --> 00:33:45,980
The clue's in the name - Janus Cars.

561
00:33:48,020 --> 00:33:50,020
Why would you be giving me a clue?

562
00:33:50,900 --> 00:33:53,260
Why does anyone do anything?

