00:34:30,620 --> 00:34:33,420
Not about. Exactly a pint. That was their first mistake.

569
00:34:33,420 --> 00:34:36,580
The blood's definitely Ian Monkford's, but it's been frozen.

570
00:34:36,580 --> 00:34:39,140
- Frozen?  - There are clear signs.

571
00:34:39,140 --> 00:34:41,980
I think Ian Monkford gave a pint of his blood some time ago

572
00:34:41,980 --> 00:34:43,450
and that's what they spread on the seat.

573
00:34:43,450 --> 00:34:46,900
- Who did?  - Janus Cars. The clue's in the name.

574
00:34:46,900 --> 00:34:49,580
- The god with two faces?  - Exactly.

575
00:34:49,580 --> 00:34:51,380
They provide a very special service.

576
00:34:51,380 --> 00:34:54,180
If you've got any kind of a problem - money troubles,

577
00:34:54,180 --> 00:34:57,820
bad marriage, whatever - Janus Cars will help you disappear.

578
00:34:57,820 --> 00:35:00,990
Ian Monkford was in some kind of trouble - financial at a guess,

579
00:35:00,990 --> 00:35:02,580
he's a banker - couldn't see a way out.

