582
00:35:08,060 --> 00:35:09,940
- So where is he?  - Colombia.

583
00:35:09,940 --> 00:35:10,740
Colombia?!

584
00:35:10,740 --> 00:35:13,100
Mr. Ewart, of Janus Cars,

585
00:35:13,100 --> 00:35:15,700
had a 20,000 Colombian peso note in his wallet.

586
00:35:15,700 --> 00:35:18,180
Quite a bit of change, too.

587
00:35:18,180 --> 00:35:20,940
He told us he hadn't been abroad recently,

588
00:35:20,940 --> 00:35:24,700
but when I asked him about the cars, I could see his tan line clearly.

589
00:35:24,700 --> 00:35:26,180
No-one wears a shirt on a sun bed.

