00:35:26,180 --> 00:35:28,140
- That, plus his arm.  - His arm?

591
00:35:28,140 --> 00:35:31,460
He kept scratching it. Obviously irritating him, and bleeding.

592
00:35:31,460 --> 00:35:34,150
Why? Because he'd recently had a booster jab. Hep-B, probably.

593
00:35:34,150 --> 00:35:35,500
Hard to tell at that distance.

594
00:35:35,500 --> 00:35:39,380
He's just back from settling Ian Monkford into his new life in Colombia.

595
00:35:39,380 --> 00:35:43,500
Mrs Monkford cashes in the life insurance, and she splits it with Janus Cars.

