628
00:37:57,860 --> 00:37:59,700
I'll give you...

629
00:38:02,780 --> 00:38:06,860
...12 hours.

630
00:38:09,380 --> 00:38:12,100
Why are you doing this?

631
00:38:13,660 --> 00:38:15,100
I like...

632
00:38:16,500 --> 00:38:19,780
...to watch you...

633
00:38:19,780 --> 00:38:21,900
dance.

634
00:38:29,460 --> 00:38:33,100
'..And I see you're back to your bad habits.'

635
00:38:33,100 --> 00:38:34,750
'...Continuing into the sudden death

636
00:38:34,750 --> 00:38:38,260
of the popular TV personality Connie Prince.

637
00:38:38,260 --> 00:38:40,660
'Miss Prince, famous for her makeover programmes,

638
00:38:40,660 --> 00:38:43,900
'was found dead two days ago by her brother in the house they shared...'

639
00:38:46,940 --> 00:38:51,220
Connie Prince, 54. She had one of those makeover shows on the telly.

640
00:38:51,220 --> 00:38:53,300
- Did you see it?  - No.

641
00:38:53,300 --> 00:38:56,580
- Very popular. She was going places.  - Not any more.

642
00:38:56,580 --> 00:38:59,900
Dead two days. According to one of her staff, Raoul de Santos,

643
00:38:59,900 --> 00:39:03,380
she cut her hand on a rusty nail in the garden. Nasty wound.

644
00:39:03,380 --> 00:39:08,060
Tetanus bacteria enters the bloodstream, good night, Vienna.

645
00:39:08,060 --> 00:39:09,940
I suppose.

646
00:39:09,940 --> 00:39:12,860
- Something's wrong with this picture.  - Eh?

647
00:39:12,860 --> 00:39:14,720
Can't be that simple, otherwise the bomber

648
00:39:14,720 --> 00:39:18,500
wouldn't be directing us towards it. Something's wrong.

649
00:39:40,420 --> 00:39:42,980
-John?  - Mm.

650
00:39:42,980 --> 00:39:46,340
Cut on her hand, it's deep. Would have bled a lot, right?

651
00:39:46,340 --> 00:39:49,340
- Yeah.  - But the wound's clean.

652
00:39:49,340 --> 00:39:51,860
Very clean, and fresh.

653
00:39:54,580 --> 00:39:57,980
How long would the bacteria have been incubating inside her?

654
00:39:57,980 --> 00:39:59,420
Oh, eight, ten days.

655
00:40:02,180 --> 00:40:03,980
The cut was made later.

656
00:40:03,980 --> 00:40:07,420
- After she was dead?  - Must have been.

657
00:40:07,420 --> 00:40:08,400
The only question is,

658
00:40:08,400 --> 00:40:12,540
how did the tetanus enter the dead woman's system?

659
00:40:12,540 --> 00:40:14,460
- You want to help, right?  - Of course.

660
00:40:14,460 --> 00:40:16,520
Connie Prince's background - family history, everything,

661
00:40:16,520 --> 00:40:18,380
- get me data.  - Right.

662
00:40:19,780 --> 00:40:23,300
- There's something else that we haven't thought of.  - Is there?

663
00:40:23,300 --> 00:40:25,860
Yes. Why is he doing this - the bomber?

664
00:40:25,860 --> 00:40:28,740
If this woman's death was suspicious, why point it up?

665
00:40:28,740 --> 00:40:31,740
- Good Samaritan.  - Who press-gangs suicide bombers?

666
00:40:31,740 --> 00:40:34,260
- Bad Samaritan.  - I'm...I'm serious, Sherlock.

667
00:40:34,260 --> 00:40:37,300
Listen, I'm cutting you slack here, I'm trusting you,

668
00:40:37,300 --> 00:40:40,740
but out there somewhere, some poor bastard's covered in Semtex

669
00:40:40,740 --> 00:40:42,940
and he's just waiting for you to solve the puzzle, so just tell me,

670
00:40:42,940 --> 00:40:45,540
what are we dealing with?

671
00:40:47,180 --> 00:40:48,860
Something new.

672
00:40:58,580 --> 00:41:02,500
Connection, connection, connection. There must be a connection.

673
00:41:02,500 --> 00:41:04,340
Carl Powers, killed 20 years ago.

