00:42:45,580 --> 00:42:49,500
- Colours?  - You know, what goes best with what.

701
00:42:49,500 --> 00:42:52,760
I should never wear cerise, apparently. Drains me.

702
00:42:53,360 --> 00:42:54,820
Who's that?

703
00:42:54,820 --> 00:42:56,100
- Home Office.  - Home Office?

704
00:42:56,100 --> 00:42:58,630
Well, Home Secretary, actually. Owes me a favour.

705
00:42:58,630 --> 00:43:02,700
A pretty girl, but she messed about with herself too much.

706
00:43:02,700 --> 00:43:06,080
They all do these days. People can hardly move their faces.

707
00:43:06,080 --> 00:43:07,460
It's silly, isn't it?

708
00:43:09,060 --> 00:43:12,260
- Did you ever see her show?  - Not until now.

709
00:43:16,340 --> 00:43:18,180
'You look pasty, love.

