00:44:28,020 --> 00:44:30,660
You'll need to pick up some stuff first. Got a pen?

731
00:44:30,660 --> 00:44:31,940
I'll remember.

732
00:44:33,460 --> 00:44:35,100
- That'll be him. - What?

733
00:44:35,100 --> 00:44:38,620
- Ah, Mr Prince, isn't it? - Yes.

734
00:44:38,620 --> 00:44:40,820
- Very good to meet you. - Yes, thank you.

735
00:44:40,820 --> 00:44:43,380
- So sorry to hear about... - Yes, yes, very kind.

736
00:44:43,380 --> 00:44:46,060
Shall we, er...?

737
00:44:46,060 --> 00:44:46,610
You were right,

738
00:44:46,610 --> 00:44:48,780
the bacteria got into her another way.

