00:44:50,420 --> 00:44:53,300
- Right, are we all set? - Er, yes. Shall we, um...?

741
00:44:56,100 --> 00:44:58,820
Not too close. I'm raw from crying.

742
00:44:58,820 --> 00:44:59,980
Oh, who's this?

743
00:44:59,980 --> 00:45:02,940
Sekhmet. Named after the Egyptian goddess.

744
00:45:02,940 --> 00:45:05,140
How nice. Was she Connie's?

745
00:45:05,140 --> 00:45:07,220
Yes, a little present from yours truly.

